column5: Ok I had several requests to post updates on my latest Project and I don't want to search back a month to find that thread so here goes. Posted in General topics as thats where they seen them--normally it's in foto section.  Painting will be done soon and then the skull cap needs attention.  Bushart
Only one word can explain this awesome art work..... PRICELESS   :worthy: Keep up to excellent work bushart!!! Leechman
very nice...don't think my wife would allow it in the house... but nice nonetheless!
Thanks guys---those antlers are tougher than you can imagine to paint on----rough lines and curves where you don't need them.  Bushart
Very, very cool Bushart, thanks for sharing that.
